snippet.title: What is Decay Factor, Decay Rate, Growth Factor, Growth Rate?
snippet.description:
Learn the difference between decay factor, decay rate, growth factor and growth rate in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.  We also discuss some examples.

1:30 Example of decay rate and the decay factor
